# lie-detector

project based on arduino
A lie detector.

components required :
	1) Arduino Diecimila or Duemilanove board or clone 1
	2) R1-3 100 K 0.5W metal film resistor 
	3) R4 470 K 0.5W metal film resistor 
	4) R5 100 K variable resistor 
	5) D1 RGB LED (common anode)
	6) S1 Piezotransducer
	7) LiquidCrystalDisplay (LCD)
